com.quinsoft.zeidon

Interface CacheMap

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ObjectEngine, Task, View
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CacheMapImpl, EntityDef, JavaObjectEngine, ObjectEngineForwarder, ViewForwarder

    public interface CacheMap
    Cache maps are a way to store objects in Zeidon objects in a thread-safe way. The key is a class object to help reduce the number of possible key collisions.
    Author:
    DG
